Mae Busch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mae_Busch 0 Mae Busch (18 June 1891 – 20 April 1946) was an Australian-born actress who worked in both silent and sound films in early Hollywood. In the latter part of her career, she appeared in many Laurel and Hardy comedies, where she frequently played Hardy's shrewish wife.
